              <span id="reviewTextContainer1841792974" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12624589828213719466">Aidan has been telling me to read this since his Honors English class read it in October. I finally picked it up (to better understand the essay he wrote about it) and devoured it in an hour or two. Talk about dense story-telling! Closer to poetry in a way, capturing so much in so few words. I will never forget Troy, who reminded me of a more-alive version of Willy Loman. Highly recommended.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


